<lb n="2"/><hi rend="grantha">śrī</hi> kopperuñciṅkatevarkku yāṇṭu <num value="27">2 <g type="numeral">10</g> 7</num><g ref="sym:dash" type="punctuation"/>vatu me<hi rend="grantha">ṣa</hi>nāyaṟṟu pū<hi rend="grantha">rvva(pa)kṣa</hi> ttu veḷḷi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>kkiḻamaiyum <hi rend="grantha">tṛti</hi> yaiyum peṟṟa <hi rend="grantha">mṛgaśīr ṣa</hi>ttu nāḷ Avaṉiāḷappiṟantāṉ nilakaṅkaraiyar
<lb n="4"/>nampirāṭṭiyār naṅkaiyāḻvār nāyaṉārkku Uṭaiyār tiruvaṇṇāmalaiuṭaiya nāya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>ṉār koyil <hi rend="grantha">śrīmāheśvara</hi> k kaṇkāṇiceyvarkaḷum tevakaṉmi koyil(k) kaṇakkarum Ivva
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṉaivom kal veṭṭi<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied> kuṭuttaparicāvatu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> Ivarperāl Eḻuntaruḷuvikkiṟa naṅkaiyā<unclear>ḻvī</unclear>cura
