<lb n="8" break="no"/><hi rend="grantha">śva</hi> rapperuvilaiyāka nāṅkaḷ viṟṟukkuṭutta Iṭamāvatu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> tirukkāmakkoṭṭamuṭai<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied> tampirāṭṭiyār koyilu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>kkut teṟku<unclear>t</unclear> tirumalaiyārkūṭattukku vaṭakku virākaraṉ tirumatiḷukkuk kiḻakku vāṇātarāyaṉ tirumataḷil<note n="55-2">Read matiḷil.</note>vaṭame
<lb n="10" break="no"/>lai mūlaikku meṟku Innāṉkellaik kuḷppaṭṭa Iṭattil viṟṟukkuṭutta patiṉālaṭikkolāl kuḻi <num value="13"><g type="numeral">10</g> 3</num> I Ikku
